title: Stadia Changelog: Five Nights at Freddy’s announced, Hot Wheels Unleashed could be next
content:
Google Stadia’s release pace didn’t get any better this week, but there’s quite a bit to look forward to. This week, Stadia confirmed a release for Five Nights at Freddy’s, and there was also a hint that Hot Wheels Unleashed could also be coming.

more…

The post Stadia Changelog: Five Nights at Freddy’s announced, Hot Wheels Unleashed could be next appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: A ratings board has hinted strongly that Hot Wheels Unleashed may soon be on its way to Google Stadia, along with other new titles.
